findModifierPragma

public static javafe.ast.ModifierPragma findModifierPragma(javafe.ast.GenericVarDecl vdecl,
                                                           int tag)
Finds and returns the first modifier pragma of vdecl that has the tag tag, if any. If none, returns null.

Note, if you want to know whether a variable is non_null or nullable (outside of called within AnnotationHandler, of course), use method escjava.AnnotationHandler.getNonNullAndNullable(javafe.ast.RoutineDecl) instead, for it properly handles inheritance of non_null and nullable pragmas.
